        <content type="html"><![CDATA[ <style>            @-webkit-keyframes masked-animation {                0% {                    background-position: 0 0                }                to {                    background-position: -100% 0                }            }             .Link {                margin: 200px auto;                font-size: 14px;                background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, #cccc39, #ff9800 25%, #cddc39 50%, #ff9800 75%, #cddc39);                -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;                -webkit-background-clip: text;                -webkit-background-size: 200% 100%;                -webkit-animation: masked-animation 2s infinite linear;            }</style><h1 id="书籍分享"><a href="#书籍分享" class="headerlink" title="书籍分享"></a>书籍分享</h1><h3>    个人整理的一些专业书籍(PDF),共享给大家。</h3><p calss="Link">注意:手机下载需要百度网盘APP.</p><h2 id="C语言区域-1-《C程序设计语言-第2版-》-C语言之父的著作，被称为C语言的的圣经。"><a href="#C语言区域-1-《C程序设计语言-第2版-》-C语言之父的著作，被称为C语言的的圣经。" class="headerlink" title="C语言区域 1.《C程序设计语言(第2版)》 C语言之父的著作，被称为C语言的的圣经。"></a>C语言区域<h3> 1.《C程序设计语言(第2版)》</h3> <b>C语言之父的著作，被称为C语言的的圣经。</b></h2><p> <img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/C%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%28%E7%AC%AC2%E7%89%88_%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%29_1.jpg_compressed.jpg" alt="C程序设计语言(第2版)"> <a style="" href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1x6LsANPgrAa1lTZU6HQyHA" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:6it6</a> <br/></p><h3>2.《C primer plus 》</h3><b>被誉为“C 语言百科全书”针对 C11 标准库更新</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/C%2BPrimer%2BPlus%E7%AC%AC6%E7%89%88_1.png_compressed.png"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1CB5KJWfAZP7boFkFNw5hCQ" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:gj64</a></p><h3>3.《C语言趣味编程100例》</h3><b>讲解了常见的一些题目思路</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/C%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E8%B6%A3%E5%91%B3%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B100%E4%BE%8B_1.jpg_compressed.jpg"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/15_SR2ErlIvM6INmJNKo7ig" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:trqw</a></p><h3>4.《征服C指针》</h3><b>从C语言指针的概念讲起，通过实验一步一步地为我们解释了指针和数组、内存、数据结构的关系，展现了指针的常见用法，揭示了各种使用技巧。</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/%E5%BE%81%E6%9C%8D%20C%20%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88%20by%20%E5%89%8D%E6%A9%8B%E5%92%8C%E5%BC%A5%20%28z-lib.org%29_1.png_compressed.png"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1J8hnIECg70h7SyNfn5wC3Q" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:qyj3</a></p><h3>5.《你必须知道的495个C语言问题》</h3><b>没看过</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/%E4%BD%A0%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84495%E4%B8%AAC%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98_1.png_compressed.png"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/13JSJDfCqqKkDHVvu9pXxLA" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:w61u</a></p><h3>6.《工程问题C语言求解  原书第4版》</h3><b>没看过</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98C%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E6%B1%82%E8%A7%A3%20%20%E5%8E%9F%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC4%E7%89%88%20by%20%EF%BC%88%E7%BE%8E%EF%BC%89%E5%BE%B7%E6%B4%9B%E8%8E%89%E4%B8%9DM.%E5%9F%83%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%E8%91%97%20%28z-lib.org%29_1.png_compressed.png"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1KEctqG-wdoTG__LOiDRvrA" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:2ht4</a></p><h2 id="Java"><a href="#Java" class="headerlink" title="Java"></a>Java</h2><h3>1.《Java编程思想第4版》</h3><b>请食用，没看过.</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/Java%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%28%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E7%AC%AC4%E7%89%88%29_1.jpg_compressed.jpg"><br><a href="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/Java%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%28%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E7%AC%AC4%E7%89%88%29_1.jpg_compressed.jpg" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:j8tw</a></p><h3>2.《疯狂Java讲义第3版》</h3><b>JDK版本为8</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/%E3%80%8A%E7%96%AF%E7%8B%82Java%E8%AE%B2%E4%B9%89%28%E7%AC%AC3%E7%89%88%29%E3%80%8B.%28%E6%9D%8E%E5%88%9A%29.%5BPDF%5D%40jb51.net_2.jpg_compressed.jpg"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1s05vvkxU-JXvqFhEtE2Hfg" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:ydwg</a></p><h2 id="Web-Area"><a href="#Web-Area" class="headerlink" title="Web Area"></a>Web Area</h2><h3 >1.《HTML5布局之路》</h3><b>从开发实战的视角，介绍了网站制作知识和开发流程。</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/HTML5%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF_1.jpg_compressed.jpg"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1r6_FbhNrnfh-XHQY2vRjSg" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:qaws</a></p><h2 id="算法"><a href="#算法" class="headerlink" title="算法"></a>算法</h2><h2 id="Java-1"><a href="#Java-1" class="headerlink" title="Java"></a>Java</h2><h3>1.《算法导论第3版》</h3><b>算法程序的灵魂</b><p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%AF%BC%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%88%E5%8E%9F%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC3%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89%20by%20Thomas%20H.Cormen%2CCharles%20E.Leiserson%2CRonald%20L.Rivest%2CClifford%20Stein%20%28z-lib.org%29_1.jpg_compressed.jpg"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1OpKywRamJGVos8425b8Kgw" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:8yq5</a></p><h3>1.《漫画算法》</h3><b>趣味可看好玩</b>    <p><img src="https://my-picture-bed.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/Picture-%20bed/Book/%E6%BC%AB%E7%94%BB%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95_1.jpg_compressed.jpg"><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1YPDbM3bJzpvBDtSRQOIh6A" class="Link">百度网盘提取码:vi59</a></p><h2 id="其它"><a href="#其它" class="headerlink" title="其它"></a>其它</h2><h3>1.《批处理标准教程》</h3><b>好书！！！</b>  <p><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1HeytVGDwLHfN6oJhaqYJPw" class="Link">4vbx</a></p><h1 id="持续更新-如果提取码有误，可以联系我。"><a href="#持续更新-如果提取码有误，可以联系我。" class="headerlink" title="持续更新,如果提取码有误，可以联系我。"></a>持续更新,如果提取码有误，可以联系我。</h1>]]></content>
      
      
